    "texte_orig": "What[SP]do[SP]you[SP]think?\n[U+1208][0002][1432][NULL][NULL][0014]I[SP]want[SP]to[SP]find[SP]my[SP]true[SP]goal.[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]\n[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]I[SP]don't[SP]think[SP]about[SP]it[SP]much.[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]\n[U+1109][E2][E3][E4][NULL][NULL]\"Ms.[SP]Saeko\n[U+1113]...[1205][001E][SP]Why[SP]do[SP]you[SP]put[SP]up[SP]walls[SP]like\nthat?[SP]You[SP]look[SP]like[SP]you're[SP]in[SP]so[SP]much[SP]pain\nthat[SP]I[SP]can't[SP]bear[SP]to[SP]see[SP]it...",
