    "nom_orig": "Lisa",
    "texte_orig": "I[SP]don't[SP]believe[SP]this![1205][001E][SP]Why[SP]are[SP]you[SP]still\nwearing[SP]your[SP]emblem!?[SP]You[SP]DO[SP]know[SP]about\nthe[SP]emblem[SP]curse,[SP]right?",
