    "texte_orig": "Says[SP]here...\n[1432][NULL][NULL][0014][U+1113][SP][U+1112]:[SP]We're[SP]holding\na[SP]girl[SP]from[SP]your[SP]school[SP]hostage.[1432][NULL][NULL][0014]",
