  {
    "id": 22,
    "offset": 394298,
    "slot_size": 230,
    "data_size": 226,
    "nom_orig": "Lisa",
    "texte_orig": "Haime![SP]Seriously!?[SP]Now[SP]that's[SP]old-\nschool...[1205][001E][SP]I[SP]dunno,[SP]though,[SP]rumor[SP]has\nit[SP]this[SP]guy's[SP]really[SP]strong!",
