    "nom_orig": "Ms.[SP]Saeko",
    "texte_orig": "Ooh,[SP]is[SP]there[SP]a[SP]profession[SP]you[SP]have[SP]in[SP]mind,\nthen?[SP]Perhaps...[SP]motorcycle-related?",
