    "nom_orig": "Ms.[SP]Saeko",
    "texte_orig": "Ahh,[SP]I[SP]see![SP]You[SP]don't[SP]have[SP]a[SP]specific\ngoal[SP]in[SP]mind,[SP]but[SP]you[SP]want[SP]to[SP]follow\nyour[SP]dreams?",
